<p>
    Options for your instance of uwu_directory may be configured here. Configuration will be written to
    <code>/var/server/custom.scss</code> and <code>/var/server/config.json</code>, so ensure that your Docker
    volumes are properly configured to store these files.
</p>
<form class="gap-2">
    <hr/>
    <div class="row row-gap-2 mb-2">
        <h4>Organizational Constraints</h4>
        <p>
            In certain cases, it may be desirable to restrict registrations to a specific email domain.
            By specifying a suffix formatted like <code>@example.com</code> in the field below, all new
            registrations will be required to be suffixed with this string. The Account Description field may
            be used to set a friendly name for this restriction. For example, a suffix of <code>@gmail.com</code>
            may warrant the description <i>Google Account</i>.
        </p>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="form-floating">
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="parentOrgAccountDescription" name="parentOrgAccountDescription" placeholder="Account Description" value="{{ config("parentOrgAccountDescription")|default("") }}"/>
                <label class="form-label" for="parentOrgAccountDescription">Account Description</label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="form-floating">
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="emailSuffix" name="emailSuffix" placeholder="Email Suffix" value="{{ config("emailSuffix")|default("") }}"/>
                <label class="form-label" for="emailSuffix">Email Suffix</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div class="row row-gap-2 mb-2">
        <h4>Site Branding</h4>
        <p>
            Across the interface, two values are used for populating branded text fields: the service name
            and the organization name. The service name refers to this webpage, the product users interact with,
            and the organization name refers to you, the organization hosting the service.
        </p>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="form-floating">
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="service" name="service" placeholder="Service Name" value="{{ config("service")|default("") }}"/>
                <label class="form-label" for="service">Service Name</label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="form-floating">
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="organization" name="organization" placeholder="Organization Name" value="{{ config("organization")|default("") }}"/>
                <label class="form-label" for="organization">Organization Name</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div class="row row-gap-2 mb-2">
        <h4>Site Favicon</h4>
        <p>
            To specify or replace a favicon for your instance, paste in SVG data below.
        </p>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="form-floating">
                        <textarea
                                class="form-control font-monospace"
                                id="favicon" name="favicon"
                                placeholder="Favicon SVG" style="height: 12em; font-size: 14px;" type="text">{{ config("favicon")|default("") }}</textarea>
                <label class="form-label" for="favicon">Favicon SVG</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div class="row row-gap-2 mb-2">
        <h4>Site Accent Color</h4>
        <p>
            If desired, you may specify an accent color in RGB hex notation with a leading <code>#</code>
            or as a standard/extended named HTML color. Please ensure that a contrast ratio of at least 2.0 is
            maintained between the site background and the new color.
        </p>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="form-floating">
                <input class="form-control" type="text" id="accentColor" name="accentColor" placeholder="Accent Color" value="{{ config("accentColor")|default("") }}"/>
                <label class="form-label" for="accentColor">Accent Color</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div class="row row-gap-2 mb-2">
        <h4>Email Signature</h4>
        <p>
            To specify a custom signature for emails, draft one below. HTML formatting is
            allowed.
        </p>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="form-floating">
                        <textarea
                                class="form-control font-monospace"
                                id="emailSignature" name="emailSignature"
                                placeholder="Email Signature" style="height: 12em; font-size: 14px;" type="text">{{ config("emailSignature")|default("") }}</textarea>
                <label class="form-label" for="emailSignature">Email Signature</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button
            type="submit"
            class="btn btn-primary"
            data-request-method="POST"
            data-request-path="{{ path("api.v1.config.create") }}">
        Save
    </button>
</form>